i18n.description:
Translation overrides. Two formats are supported:

• Per-language: keys are locale codes (or the special key 'all' which applies to every language).
  e.g. { all: { header: { title: 'Bot' } }, tr: { header: { title: 'Botum' } } }

• Flat: namespaces directly — applied to every registered language.
  e.g. { header: { title: 'Bot' } }
